      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m so excited to show you this absolute gem. It\u2019s been my pride and joy and is in truly flawless shape\u2014honestly, it feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s been pampered and looks brand new inside and out, you\u2019ve found it. Come say hi and take a look; you\u2019re going to love it!",
