    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Offered here is a truly exceptional, collector-grade vehicle in pristine condition. This car has been meticulously kept in a climate-controlled garage and shows like it just rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior paint is flawless, featuring a deep, mirror-like luster protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating\u2014absolutely no rock chips, swirls, or imperfections to be found. Inside, the cabin remains in factory-fresh state; the premium leather is supple with no bolster wear, and every electronic component functions perfectly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, supported by a complete binder of service records and a recent preventative maintenance flush of all fluids. With low mileage and a history of adult ownership, this is a rare opportunity to own a turn-key example that satisfies even the most detail-oriented enthusiast.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
